Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:06.24,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}Mountains come out of the sky they stand there
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:13.44,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}Twenty four before my love and I'll be there
